               <msContents>
                  <summary>This papyrus contains the order for payment of 2 drachmas to an unnamed beneficiary. The money was paid to cover the expenses incurred by a shipment of an unnamed object or substance by the road. This shipment was made from a property owned by the brothers in the Arsinoite nome.</summary>
