   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 20, Pharmouthi 18. Give from the account of Julius Theon and Julius Theon for the expense of a shipment by the road from the Arsinoite nome, their Excellensies having come for a visit, of 12 drachmas through  the same Arapai 2 drachmas. (2nd hd.) Give the 2 drachmas."</ab>
